data.description: Concrete block home. Home is on quiet street in desirable Port St John area, and is convenient to the Kennedy Space Center, beaches, Orlando, airports and theme parks. Updated Custom Kitchen with stainless steel appliances and Granite counter tops.  Each bathroom has newer style vanities and granite tops with stylish fixtures.  The back porch looks out to a very nice and fully fenced in back yard.
